node.text:
Tell us what you’re most excited about getting during the sale, Go!

Here’s everything you need to know:

Starts AUG 6 @ 10 am CST
Ends AUG 9 @ 12 am CST 

 

• Kyte KASH/rewards can be used the 6th to the 8th

• Sunday 10AM CST Adult blankets will be added to the sale and will be $130

• Monday, the 9th, will be an automatic 15% and cannot be combined with Kyte KASH/rewards 

• Shipping/processing time is UP TO 3 WEEKS The later you order in the sale the longer it can take. 

• ALL SALES ARE FINAL

• If your children are in between sizes it is recommended to size up

• Women’s lounge dresses/Vnecks will have BOTH old and new sizing. It will state the difference as well as have a price difference

• Afterpay is always available to use but there are NO cart holds. 

• The site is locked 3 hours before the start of the sale

node.text:
Our highly anticipated lounge robe is breathable enough to wear as an outer layer or alone. An inner string keeps everything tucked in place, while the outer belt is sewn into place so it’s easy to tie and never lost.
Sizes range from xs/sm, md/lg, xl/xxl.
